## State Check (run first)

```bash
eval $(~/.claude/skills/gstack/bin/gstack-slug 2>/dev/null) || true
_PROJECT_DIR="$HOME/.gstack/projects/${SLUG:-prompt-system}"
mkdir -p "$_PROJECT_DIR"
